graph LR
    ODHCLI[odh-cli<br/>kubectl-odh / rhai-cli]

    %% Build Dependencies
    subgraph BuildDeps["Build Dependencies"]
        Go[Go 1.25]
        UBI9[ubi9/go-toolset 1.25]
        OSEBase[ose-cli-rhel9 v4.21.0]
    end

    ODHCLI -->|build lang| Go
    ODHCLI -->|builder image| UBI9
    ODHCLI -->|runtime base| OSEBase

    %% Go Library Dependencies
    subgraph GoLibs["Go Libraries"]
        Cobra[cobra v1.10.2<br/>CLI framework]
        ControllerRT[controller-runtime<br/>v0.23.1]
        ClientGo[client-go v0.35.1<br/>K8s API client]
        CLIRuntime[cli-runtime v0.35.1<br/>kubectl flags]
        OLMApi[operator-framework/api<br/>v0.39.0]
        OLMCLI[operator-lifecycle-manager<br/>v0.40.0]
        Semver[semver/v4 v4.0.0]
        GoJQ[gojq v0.12.18]
        TableWriter[tablewriter v1.1.3]
    end

    ODHCLI -->|CLI framework| Cobra
    ODHCLI -->|K8s client| ControllerRT
    ODHCLI -->|K8s API| ClientGo
    ODHCLI -->|kubectl flags| CLIRuntime
    ODHCLI -->|OLM types| OLMApi
    ODHCLI -->|OLM client| OLMCLI
    ODHCLI -->|version parse| Semver
    ODHCLI -->|JQ eval| GoJQ
    ODHCLI -->|table output| TableWriter

    %% Internal RHOAI Platform Dependencies (CRD Read)
    subgraph InternalDeps["Internal RHOAI Components (CRD Read)"]
        RHODSOp[rhods-operator<br/>DSC, DSCI]
        NotebookCtrl[odh-notebook-controller<br/>Notebooks]
        KServe[KServe<br/>ISVCs, ServingRuntimes,<br/>LLMISVCs]
        KueueComp[Kueue<br/>ClusterQueues, LocalQueues]
        DSPOp[data-science-pipelines-operator<br/>DSPA]
        TrustyAI[TrustyAI<br/>GuardrailsOrchestrator]
        RayComp[Ray / CodeFlare<br/>RayClusters, RayJobs,<br/>AppWrappers]
        TrainingOp[Training Operator<br/>PyTorchJobs]
        DashboardComp[Dashboard<br/>AcceleratorProfiles,<br/>HardwareProfiles]
        LlamaStack[LlamaStack<br/>LlamaStackDistributions]
    end

    ODHCLI -->|version, state| RHODSOp
    ODHCLI -->|backup, compat| NotebookCtrl
    ODHCLI -->|deploy mode| KServe
    ODHCLI -->|migration| KueueComp
    ODHCLI -->|renaming| DSPOp
    ODHCLI -->|validation| TrustyAI
    ODHCLI -->|removal checks| RayComp
    ODHCLI -->|deprecation| TrainingOp
    ODHCLI -->|migration| DashboardComp
    ODHCLI -->|validation| LlamaStack

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    subgraph ExternalDeps["External Platform Dependencies"]
        CertMgr[cert-manager<br/>Subscription read]
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh Operator<br/>Subscription, PackageManifest]
        Kuadrant[Kuadrant<br/>LLM-d readiness]
        Authorino[Authorino<br/>TLS readiness]
        OpenShift[OpenShift<br/>ClusterVersion >=4.19.9]
        OLM[OLM<br/>Subscriptions, CSVs,<br/>PackageManifests]
    end

    ODHCLI -->|dependency check| CertMgr
    ODHCLI -->|mesh checks| ServiceMesh
    ODHCLI -->|LLM-d gate| Kuadrant
    ODHCLI -->|TLS gate| Authorino
    ODHCLI -->|version check| OpenShift
    ODHCLI -->|operator discovery| OLM

    %% Runtime Infrastructure
    subgraph Runtime["Runtime Infrastructure"]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        LocalFS[Local Filesystem<br/>backup output]
    end

    ODHCLI -->|all queries| K8sAPI
    ODHCLI -.->|backup YAML| LocalFS

    %% Container Image Bundled Tools
    subgraph Bundled["Container Image Bundled Tools"]
        YQ[yq<br/>FIPS-compliant]
        Python3[Python 3<br/>+ kubernetes client]
        UpgradeHelpers[rhoai-upgrade-helpers<br/>Shell/Python scripts]
    end

    ODHCLI -.->|bundled| YQ
    ODHCLI -.->|bundled| Python3
    ODHCLI -.->|bundled| UpgradeHelpers

